title: Moynahan marries New York businessman
text:
Moynahan marries New York businessman Actress announces wedding via Instagram By Lisa Respers France CNN POSTED: 11:06 AM MDT Oct 18, 2015 UPDATED: 11:40 AM MDT Oct 18, 2015 Jamie McCarthy/Getty Images (CNN) - 
Actress Bridget Moynahan surprised fans recently with the news that she is now a married woman. 
The "Blue Bloods" star, who has a son with football player Tom Brady, married New York businessman Andrew Frankel at a ceremony on Saturday in the Hamptons on Long Island, New York. Moynahan posted a wedding picture on her Instagram account with the caption "Oh, by the way, guess what I just did." Related Content
